        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Partial answer...  ST has a set duration of ummm, not long, maybe 20 secs or so.  It does not wear off early and pets can no longer break the mez.</P><P>Also, ST resists seem to get better as you age, at least for me it has.  I used to feel the same way you do but now it seems fear will be resisted more often than ST.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=97736" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.facepics.com/profiles/images/alaughery/alaughery_image3.jpg" border=0></a><br>47 Gnecromancer<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
