         Ive never seen CHA raise or lower resist rates on ST. The MOBs you fight influence that of course, and I believe its magic resistance that they are rolling against to have it land/break out of it.</P><P>Charisma plays no role, when I got the spell I casted it a dozen times on blue to yellows, and then parsed the logs, with and without CHA boosting gear. It made no difference. This isnt the end all be all proof positive, but my CHA is fairly low and it hasnt mattered one bit. Sometimes I get resisted 5 in a row, sometimes it lands 10 times in and lasts for the full 18.</P><P>Kith</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
