		<img src="icon_posticon.gif" border="0" hspace="3"><font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2">Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;08/25/2002&nbsp;:&nbsp; 10:33:38</font>

		&nbsp;<a href="pop_profile.asp?mode=display&amp;id=3322"><img src="icon_profile.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Show Profile" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>
        
			&nbsp;<a href="JavaScript:openWindow('pop_mail.asp?id=3322')"><img src="icon_email.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Email Poster" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=62867&amp;TOPIC_ID=7219&amp;FORUM_ID=3&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=Necromancer+Game+Guides&amp;Topic_Title=2+Questions+for+veteran+necros&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Sallymander gave you about the most accurate answer you can get.</P><P>Charisma has never been proven to have any affect on any necro spell. Please take note of the "never been proven" part. It is currently urban legend. </P><P>Screaming Terror will ALWAYS last for 18 seconds, UNLESS the mob is damaged in any way. You are probably landing a dot on it and that is what's breaking your ST. Or your pet is breaking it. See below for an explanation on the pet.</P><P>Pets CAN break ST or any other mez spell. If the pet is in mid-swing when the ST or Mez is cast, then good ol' Jabober will finish his swing and break it. Buffed pet will do this more often. Easy enough to get around, you see "Mezzing such and such" from your enchanter then calmly hit /pet back off a couple times and promptly direct him to his target with a /pet attack afterwards. Pet control is a very important thing to learn. It has become much easier since initial release, but it is still required.</P><P>Please, unless you're sure, Quit with the false information. It's great to want to provide help, but unless you know the answer to provide that help, then you're doing nothing but a disservice to them.</P><P>~Bonez</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=264137" target="_blank" target="_blank">Charbonez Soulmark</a><BR>Duzzil Ro<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

