        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Look, it doesn't even matter if you're a necro or a chanter. Mez is Mez is Mez, and all Mez will last the full duration, unless the mob takes damage, at which point it will *always* break.</P><P>Charisma has nothing to do with enchanter or necro mez. The only thing that affects mez for either class are levels and the mob's Magic resist. Lower the magic resist, and you'll get less chance of mez resist.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
